Description copied from interface: ISmugObject
Obtains detailed information from the repository or cache for this object. Some objects require a password to obtain (part of) this detailed information (see setObjectPassword). The level of detail is determined by the current session-account. The owner of this object gets all the information. Any other account may only get part of the object's data.
